markets.title: How many sales will Play have ?
markets.rules_primary: If Play's sales, on the Hits Daily Double Top 50 Chart for September 19, 2025, are at least 900000, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: This event will specifically encompass the number listed under Albums on Hits Daily Double’s Top 50 chart for the relevant week. If data is unavailable or partially unavailable by the Expiration date, then all affected markets resolve to No.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
